1.2.name: wordpress/jumbo-mortgage-rates
1.2.description: This plugin installs a customizable Jumbo Mortgage Rates Widget that you can drag into your sidebar in the widget area of wordpress. The Jumbo mortgage rates widget is updated daily by FreeRateUpdate.com who researches wholesale mortgage lender's rate sheets and updates their Jumbo mortgage rates multiple times per day.
